title: Seneville Cafe
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Juice bar, Take-out, Bakery, European, Romanian, Non-veg
description: Bakery cafe with multiple outlets around the city. Sells bread, cakes, sandwiches, drinks (including fresh juices) and coffee. Most of the bread is vegan, some cakes are vegan including: pastel (apple tart with cinammon), amorino (belgian chocolate tart), afinel (blueberry and chocolate cake), cocosana (coconut and chocolate roll), and the apple/poppy seed/pumpkin pies. Always ask for the vegan options (try the Romanian word "de post").
